  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5695204">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5695204/" class="title-link">有时间的话，还是听节目吧</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5695204"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2836205/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2836205/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">黄色潜水艇</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-12"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-12 14:59:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5695204_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  很多很好的观点，都是两个人在节目里你来我往的谈话中碰撞出来的。 现在写成这种文体，反倒是看起来有不是很连贯的感觉。  而且好像两个人在这本书上没有花太多的心思，很多观点和案例在一本书里居然重复的使用。读起来很啰嗦。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5695204/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
